{"ID":64,"post_author":"1","post_date":"2026-01-08 22:39:22","post_date_gmt":"2026-01-08 22:39:22","post_content":"<h1>Hire vetted software engineers in the Baltics and Northern Europe<\/h1>\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Multi-step screening by technical experts. Clear process. Fast shortlist delivery.<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"\/request-candidates\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRequest Candidates\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>How it Works<\/h2>\t\t<p>A straightforward process designed for busy technical leaders<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M336 64h-80c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64s-64 28.7-64 64H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v352c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h288c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V112c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM192 40c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24-24-10.7-24-24 10.7-24 24-24zm121.2 231.8l-143 141.8c-4.7 4.7-12.3 4.6-17-.1l-82.6-83.3c-4.7-4.7-4.6-12.3.1-17L99.1 285c4.7-4.7 12.3-4.6 17 .1l46 46.4 106-105.2c4.7-4.7 12.3-4.6 17 .1l28.2 28.4c4.7 4.8 4.6 12.3-.1 17z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTell us what you need\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tShare your role requirements, tech stack, and timeline. Just 5 minutes to fill a brief online form or a short discovery call for complex roles.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M505 442.7L405.3 343c-4.5-4.5-10.6-7-17-7H372c27.6-35.3 44-79.7 44-128C416 93.1 322.9 0 208 0S0 93.1 0 208s93.1 208 208 208c48.3 0 92.7-16.4 128-44v16.3c0 6.4 2.5 12.5 7 17l99.7 99.7c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0l28.3-28.3c9.4-9.4 9.4-24.6.1-34zM208 336c-70.7 0-128-57.2-128-128 0-70.7 57.2-128 128-128 70.7 0 128 57.2 128 128 0 70.7-57.2 128-128 128z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWe source and screen\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMulti-step technical screening process\nSkills assessment and technical interviews\nBackground verification and reference checks.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M96,128A64,64,0,1,0,32,64,64,64,0,0,0,96,128Zm0,176.08a44.11,44.11,0,0,1,13.64-32L181.77,204c1.65-1.55,3.77-2.31,5.61-3.57A63.91,63.91,0,0,0,128,160H64A64,64,0,0,0,0,224v96a32,32,0,0,0,32,32V480a32,32,0,0,0,32,32h64a32,32,0,0,0,32-32V383.61l-50.36-47.53A44.08,44.08,0,0,1,96,304.08ZM480,128a64,64,0,1,0-64-64A64,64,0,0,0,480,128Zm32,32H448a63.91,63.91,0,0,0-59.38,40.42c1.84,1.27,4,2,5.62,3.59l72.12,68.06a44.37,44.37,0,0,1,0,64L416,383.62V480a32,32,0,0,0,32,32h64a32,32,0,0,0,32-32V352a32,32,0,0,0,32-32V224A64,64,0,0,0,512,160ZM444.4,295.34l-72.12-68.06A12,12,0,0,0,352,236v36H224V236a12,12,0,0,0-20.28-8.73L131.6,295.34a12.4,12.4,0,0,0,0,17.47l72.12,68.07A12,12,0,0,0,224,372.14V336H352v36.14a12,12,0,0,0,20.28,8.74l72.12-68.07A12.4,12.4,0,0,0,444.4,295.34Z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMeet your shortlist\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tReceive pre-screened candidate\nprofiles with assessment notes.\nSchedule interviews directly with candidates\nOngoing support throughout the hiring process\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Our Specialties<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M537.6 226.6c4.1-10.7 6.4-22.4 6.4-34.6 0-53-43-96-96-96-19.7 0-38.1 6-53.3 16.2C367 64.2 315.3 32 256 32c-88.4 0-160 71.6-160 160 0 2.7.1 5.4.2 8.1C40.2 219.8 0 273.2 0 336c0 79.5 64.5 144 144 144h368c70.7 0 128-57.3 128-128 0-61.9-44-113.6-102.4-125.4z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCloud Backend\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJava \/ Spring Boot \/ Kotlin\n??? Python \/ Django \/ FastAPI\n??? Go \/ Rust (emerging)\n??? Microservices, REST APIs, Message Queues\n??? AWS \/ Azure \/ GCP\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 496 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M336.5 160C322 70.7 287.8 8 248 8s-74 62.7-88.5 152h177zM152 256c0 22.2 1.2 43.5 3.3 64h185.3c2.1-20.5 3.3-41.8 3.3-64s-1.2-43.5-3.3-64H155.3c-2.1 20.5-3.3 41.8-3.3 64zm324.7-96c-28.6-67.9-86.5-120.4-158-141.6 24.4 33.8 41.2 84.7 50 141.6h108zM177.2 18.4C105.8 39.6 47.8 92.1 19.3 160h108c8.7-56.9 25.5-107.8 49.9-141.6zM487.4 192H372.7c2.1 21 3.3 42.5 3.3 64s-1.2 43-3.3 64h114.6c5.5-20.5 8.6-41.8 8.6-64s-3.1-43.5-8.5-64zM120 256c0-21.5 1.2-43 3.3-64H8.6C3.2 212.5 0 233.8 0 256s3.2 43.5 8.6 64h114.6c-2-21-3.2-42.5-3.2-64zm39.5 96c14.5 89.3 48.7 152 88.5 152s74-62.7 88.5-152h-177zm159.3 141.6c71.4-21.2 129.4-73.7 158-141.6h-108c-8.8 56.9-25.6 107.8-50 141.6zM19.3 352c28.6 67.9 86.5 120.4 158 141.6-24.4-33.8-41.2-84.7-50-141.6h-108z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFullstack\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tReact \/ Angular \/ Vue.js\n??? Node.js \/ TypeScript\n??? Next.js \/ Nuxt.js\n??? Modern CSS frameworks\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M480 160H32c-17.673 0-32-14.327-32-32V64c0-17.673 14.327-32 32-32h448c17.673 0 32 14.327 32 32v64c0 17.673-14.327 32-32 32zm-48-88c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24zm-64 0c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24zm112 248H32c-17.673 0-32-14.327-32-32v-64c0-17.673 14.327-32 32-32h448c17.673 0 32 14.327 32 32v64c0 17.673-14.327 32-32 32zm-48-88c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24zm-64 0c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24zm112 248H32c-17.673 0-32-14.327-32-32v-64c0-17.673 14.327-32 32-32h448c17.673 0 32 14.327 32 32v64c0 17.673-14.327 32-32 32zm-48-88c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24zm-64 0c-13.255 0-24 10.745-24 24s10.745 24 24 24 24-10.745 24-24-10.745-24-24-24z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDevOps &amp; Infra\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t??? Kubernetes \/ Docker \/ Container orchestration\n??? CI\/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Jenkins)\n??? Infrastructure as Code (Terraform, Ansible)\n??? Cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP)\n??? Monitoring and observability\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M202.021 0C122.202 0 70.503 32.703 29.914 91.026c-7.363 10.58-5.093 25.086 5.178 32.874l43.138 32.709c10.373 7.865 25.132 6.026 33.253-4.148 25.049-31.381 43.63-49.449 82.757-49.449 30.764 0 68.816 19.799 68.816 49.631 0 22.552-18.617 34.134-48.993 51.164-35.423 19.86-82.299 44.576-82.299 106.405V320c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h72.471c13.255 0 24-10.745 24-24v-5.773c0-42.86 125.268-44.645 125.268-160.627C377.504 66.256 286.902 0 202.021 0zM192 373.459c-38.196 0-69.271 31.075-69.271 69.271 0 38.195 31.075 69.27 69.271 69.27s69.271-31.075 69.271-69.271-31.075-69.27-69.271-69.27z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSomething else in mind?\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tHave a different technical need?\nContact us to discuss your requirements.\nWe expand our network based on client needs.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Why our team is your best choice?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M400 480H48c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48V80c0-26.51 21.49-48 48-48h352c26.51 0 48 21.49 48 48v352c0 26.51-21.49 48-48 48zm-204.686-98.059l184-184c6.248-6.248 6.248-16.379 0-22.627l-22.627-22.627c-6.248-6.248-16.379-6.249-22.628 0L184 302.745l-70.059-70.059c-6.248-6.248-16.379-6.248-22.628 0l-22.627 22.627c-6.248 6.248-6.248 16.379 0 22.627l104 104c6.249 6.25 16.379 6.25 22.628.001z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMulti-Step Technical Screening\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t??? Technical assessment by practitioners\n??? Hands-on coding challenges\n??? System design discussions\n??? Cultural fit evaluation\n??? Not just CV matching\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 496 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M248 8C111.03 8 0 119.03 0 256s111.03 248 248 248 248-111.03 248-248S384.97 8 248 8zm0 432c-101.69 0-184-82.29-184-184 0-101.69 82.29-184 184-184 101.69 0 184 82.29 184 184 0 101.69-82.29 184-184 184zm0-312c-70.69 0-128 57.31-128 128s57.31 128 128 128 128-57.31 128-128-57.31-128-128-128zm0 192c-35.29 0-64-28.71-64-64s28.71-64 64-64 64 28.71 64 64-28.71 64-64 64z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFocus on Quality Over Quantity\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t??? Curated shortlists (3-5 candidates)\n??? Only candidates who meet your requirements\n??? No \"spray and pray\" approach\n??? Save time on unqualified interviews\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M256,8C119,8,8,119,8,256S119,504,256,504,504,393,504,256,393,8,256,8Zm92.49,313h0l-20,25a16,16,0,0,1-22.49,2.5h0l-67-49.72a40,40,0,0,1-15-31.23V112a16,16,0,0,1,16-16h32a16,16,0,0,1,16,16V256l58,42.5A16,16,0,0,1,348.49,321Z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFast Turnaround\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t??? 7-14 day typical delivery timeline\n??? Responsive communication\n??? Clear progress updates\n??? Flexible engagement model\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M172.268 501.67C26.97 291.031 0 269.413 0 1